= Variables

:My name: Alex Efros
My name is {myname}

Escaped: \{myname} and +++{myname}+++

= Images & videos

.Caption to an image with figure
image::https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/35/Tux.svg[250,350]
//in brackets write dimensions - first number is width and second one is height

:figure-caption!:
.Caption to an image without figure
image::https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/35/Tux.svg[250,350]

image::name-of-image.png[]

.Caption to a video
video::video_file.mp4[]

.Embedding a YouTube video
video::rPQoq7ThGAU[youtube,600,400]
//in brackets write youtube as source, first number is width and second one is height


